data.description: Spacious Two story home with Four Bedrooms, 3 FULL Bathrooms, a Two Car Garage with open Living Space, Kitchen with large pantry, lots of cabinets, an Island for additional seating, formal dining area, Covered Patio, generous size Utility Room and a Gameroom. Bedroom 1 is separate from other rooms and comes with a Large Closet. Plan offers TWO BEDROOMS DOWN AND TWO BEDROOMS UP, high ceilings, recessed lighting, coat closet, and lots of storage space. Espresso colored cabinetry, home automation system included! Ask about available New Home Standard Features within our community.
